      <title>SEC 加密货币监管、交易所、ETF 专员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/sec-commissioner-on-crypto-regulation-exchanges-etfs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SEC 加密货币工作组负责人兼 SEC 委员 Hester Peirce 讨论了加密货币监管、创新、交易所备案、模因币、ETF、与 CFTC 的合作以及前 SEC 委员 Gary Gensler 任职期间正在进行的执法案件。她与 Tim Stenovec 和 Sonali Basak 就“Bloomberg Crypto”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/sec-commissioner-on-crypto-regulation-exchanges-etfs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:02:21 GMT</pubDate>
