      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通预计第一季度交易和投资银行业务将大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/jpmorgan-sees-trading-investment-banking-jumps-in-first-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着华尔街继续受益于波动性和资本市场的复苏，摩根大通公司第一季度的交易收入和投资银行费用可能均会增长 10% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/jpmorgan-sees-trading-investment-banking-jumps-in-first-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:55:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>产量增长强劲，全球石油供应过剩加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/global-oil-glut-seen-expanding-on-stronger-production-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国预计今年和2026年的石油盈余将比此前预测的要大，这得益于美国和非欧佩克国家石油产量的持续增长，且预计制裁不太可能影响俄罗斯的石油产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/global-oil-glut-seen-expanding-on-stronger-production-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的儿子支持朋友的一分钱股票，促使价格上涨84％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-s-sons-back-friend-s-penny-stock-spurring-84-price-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的两个儿子正在投资于总部位于特朗普大厦（Trump Tower）的小型，无利可图的生物技术公司将投资银行转变为投资银行，这增加了第一个家庭在其自身轨道内越来越多的商业利益清单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-s-sons-back-friend-s-penny-stock-spurring-84-price-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“给我钱”：创纪录的金价对顶级矿业公司来说是一个考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/-show-me-the-money-record-gold-price-is-test-for-top-miners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金价徘徊在历史高位附近，但巴里克黄金公司和纽蒙特公司未能利用黄金价格上涨的机会，令投资者感到失望。未来 10 天将是顶级生产商赢回持怀疑态度的股东的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/-show-me-the-money-record-gold-price-is-test-for-top-miners</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:49:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部长称津巴布韦尚未准备好采用单一货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/zimbabwe-isn-t-yet-ready-for-a-sole-currency-finance-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦财政部长姆图利·恩库贝 (Mthuli Ncube) 表示，这个南部非洲国家需要重新获得信贷额度，然后才能采用津巴布韦元作为其唯一货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/zimbabwe-isn-t-yet-ready-for-a-sole-currency-finance-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
